name: Zavi (FROM THE COLLECTION XXIII SERIES)
description: She is casual glam. Loves bright colors almost as vivid as her imagination, she is shy at times but cares deeply for the world, she lives in Japan, fall season has just begun. She is a student at a local college and walks campus through a beautiful nature path, it's October and it has rained down flowers. purple and white flowers. She is the ultimate eccentric IT Girl.
